{
    "poem_title": "-LXVII-",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": true,
    "author": "Gongora",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "¿Para qué dime Marcia, te perfumas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--++-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "y en tantos alambiques y redomas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "de Pancaya destilas los aromas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "y al pájaro del Sol cuentas las plumas?",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---++--+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "¿Para qué dime Marcia, te perfumas,\ny en tantos alambiques y redomas,\nde Pancaya destilas los aromas,\ny al pájaro del Sol cuentas las plumas?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "Si eres mujer común, no te presumas",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "empresas de Cartagos, y de Romas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "si tales son las que a tu cargo tomas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "para charco te bastan las espumas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si eres mujer común, no te presumas\nempresas de Cartagos, y de Romas,\nsi tales son las que a tu cargo tomas,\npara charco te bastan las espumas."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Que mal podrás del bálsamo Guineo",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "desmentir las ofensas al olfato",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "con todo lo fenicio y los Sabeo.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que mal podrás del bálsamo Guineo\ndesmentir las ofensas al olfato\ncon todo lo fenicio y los Sabeo."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "Mientras te taraceas cada rato,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-----+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "que juntas en adúltero Himeneo,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "al marfil terso, el ébano mulato.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--++-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mientras te taraceas cada rato,\nque juntas en adúltero Himeneo,\nal marfil terso, el ébano mulato."
        }
    ]
}